            <p class="card-text" style="text-align:left">Our Marketing Consulting goal is to help our clients achieve sustainable business growth through market intelligence, creativity, and strategic vision. We want to help customers build an organization that attracts, develops, and retains outstanding people.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body alert-info">
