                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
                <div class="panel panel-default text-center">
                    <div class="panel-heading">
                        <h2>Amazon</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body alert-info">
                        <p>An extremely competent team that knows the ever-changing challenge of optimization on Google. They have done an incredible job of not just helping us with SEO, but keeping us updated. There’s never a long period of silence. They always keep us in the loop, and we can say we’ve seen a noticeable increase in traffic thanks to their work.</p>
                        <p><strong>- Tom Hanks, Global Marketing Head, Amazon USA</strong></p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
                <div class="panel panel-default text-center">
                    <div class="panel-heading ">
                        <h2>Spotify</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel-body alert-info">
                        <p>We could not be more pleased working with TAG! We have been working with their team for quite some time, and they have continually gone above and beyond year after year. Collaborating with TAG has resulted in the most effective return on investment for our marketing budget.</p>
                        <p><strong>- Shahrukh Khan, CEO, Spotify</strong></p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    

